    "extraction_notes": "Table 1c (Pharmacokinetic) of the Amgen AMG 416 Schedule of Assessments. domain table sharing Table 1a's 20-visit timeline. 'Central Laboratory' is a level-0 section header; the six 'PK' rows (level 1) differ only by the 'Time' qualifier, which is folded into activity_name (cell_text kept as raw 'PK'). Could alternatively be argued 'subsidiary' (finer within-visit PK timing) but shares the exact day columns, so classified domain per the taxonomy's Amgen example. 29/ET header carries marker a; its footnote text is NOT restated on page 36 - reused from the shared Day-29-withdrawal footnote (pages 33/35) and flagged. All cells X."
  },
